headline: Franklin Small-Mid Cap Growth Fund Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: US stocks collectively rose in the fourth quarter of 2024, with the S&P 500 Index, Dow Jones Industrial Average and NASDAQ Composite Index reaching new record highs.
